D. Code

✅ Answer: B
📘 Explanation: Structured lists reduce confusion.

17. Lists improve:

A. Randomness
B. Readability
C. Errors
D. Complexity

✅ Answer: B
📘 Explanation: Easier to read and parse.

18. AI prefers lists because they are:

A. Decorative
